
Overview of verb repay

The verb repay has 4 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (7) refund, return, repay, give back -- (pay back; "Please refund me my money")
2. (1) requite, repay -- (make repayment for or return something)
3. reward, repay, pay back -- (act or give recompense in recognition of someone's behavior or actions)
4. retort, come back, repay, return, riposte, rejoin -- (answer back)
